txt.en: Gauredain out of the northern wilds of Forochel have come south to the Trollshaws, answering the call of Mordor.
Gauredain are encamped at Echad Gauradan in Tâl Bruinen, in the Trollshaws.\n\nWhile in Tâl Bruinen, you should defeat the Gauredain who have encamped there.
